5|$|American {{rock band}} Evanescence has {{released}} four studio albums, one live album, one compilation album, one demo album, three extended plays, 13 singles, six promotional singles, and 12 music videos. Evanescence was formed <b>in</b> <b>Little</b> <b>Rock,</b> Arkansas in 1995 by Amy Lee and Ben Moody. The lineup {{of the band}} has since gone through numerous changes with Lee being the principal member. To date, the band has sold nearly 25 million albums worldwide.|$|E
