50|$|River Cities Travel Center (RCTC) {{opened on}} August 28, 2000, {{to serve as}} the main {{transfer}} hub <b>in</b> downtown <b>Little</b> <b>Rock.</b> As of January 2016, a total of 22 fixed routes and all four express routes serve RCTC, which doubles as the agency's primary sales and information office for riders. At the Midtown Target stop <b>in</b> central <b>Little</b> <b>Rock,</b> five fixed routes (#3, #5, #8, #9, and #22) converge on Midtown Avenue to provide more convenient, efficient transferring opportunities <b>in</b> west-central <b>Little</b> <b>Rock.</b>|$|R
